🎥 Project Demonstration
Project Demo Overview

The project demonstration showcases the complete workflow of the application, including voice input processing, concept analysis, semantic similarity evaluation, and result generation.

Demo Highlights
User uploads or records voice input.
Speech-to-Text module converts audio into text.
Extracted text is analyzed using AI/NLP techniques.
Semantic similarity engine compares the response with expected concepts.
Audio features such as fluency and clarity are evaluated.
The system generates scores and feedback reports.
Interactive dashboard displays analysis results and visualizations.
Demonstrated Features

✅ User-friendly interface
✅ Real-time speech processing
✅ AI-based concept understanding evaluation
✅ Performance scoring and feedback generation
✅ Data visualization and report generation
✅ End-to-end workflow execution

Technologies Demonstrated
Python
Streamlit
Google Gemini API
Speech Recognition Libraries
Natural Language Processing (NLP)
Machine Learning Techniques
